OL,3,C'Spider in hallway': Shocking examples
OL,4,Cof timewasting 999 emergency calls
OL,6,FShocking figures show just 15 per cent
OL,7,Fof 999 calls made to the Met Police
OL,8,Fare genuine emergencies, as officers
OL,9,Fremind the public to only call in
OL,10,Furgent or life-threatening situations.
OL,12,FA woman scared of a spider in her
OL,13,Fhallway, a driver who had problems
OL,14,Fcharging his electric car and people
OL,15,Ffrustrated by delivery drivers not
OL,16,Fturning up are just a few examples of
OL,17,Fnon-urgent calls.
