OL,3,C'Spider in hallway': Shocking examples
OL,4,Cof timewasting 999 emergency calls
OL,6,FThe Met says such calls take up
OL,7,Fvaluable call handler time and stop
OL,8,Fstaff dealing with genuine emergencies
OL,9,Fand doing their job keeping Londoners
OL,10,Fsafe.
OL,12,FThe Metropolitan Police Service is
OL,13,Ftoday telling Londoners they will
OL,14,Falways be available 24/7 to respond to
OL,15,Fgenuine 999 emergencies, but is urging
OL,16,Fthe public to think before they call.
