OL,3,C'Spider in hallway': Shocking examples
OL,4,Cof timewasting 999 emergency calls
OL,6,FPeople should always call 999 when:
OL,8,F-A crime is in progress
OL,10,F-There is threat to life
OL,12,F-Someone is in immediate danger
OL,14,FWhen is the right time to call 101?
OL,16,F-To report a crime that has previously
OL,17,Fhappened
OL,19,F-Low-level situations such as a noise
OL,20,Fcomplaint or minor anti-social
OL,21,Fbehaviour
