OL,3,C'Spider in hallway': Shocking examples
OL,4,Cof timewasting 999 emergency calls
OL,6,FThose who accidentally call 999 are
OL,7,Fasked to stay on the phone until they
OL,8,Fhave spoken to an operator, otherwise
OL,9,Fhandlers have to spend time
OL,10,Fundertaking a risk assessment to make
OL,11,Fsure the person who called isn't in
OL,12,Fdanger.
